    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807950/extras/410e59d73759ba66292843a04230f441.poster.avif?t=1753743460\" width=534 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807950/extras/410e59d73759ba66292843a04230f441.webm?t=1753743460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807950/extras/410e59d73759ba66292843a04230f441.mp4?t=1753743460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>&quot;时光翻转器&quot;是一款冒险/探索游戏，设定在一个类似地球的隐秘维度中。<br>通过时光翻转装置，你可以在两个世界状态之间切换：过去和未来。这个强大的工具将帮助你穿越这个世界，找到隐藏的通道、物品，并寻找失踪的人，那些被外星实体绑架的人。解救他们，他们将帮助你逃脱。不过要小心，会有抵抗。<br><br>&quot;主要特点：<br><br>    一个需要自己探索的地方，没有任何指导，充满惊喜、超现实主义和超凡脱俗的事物。<br>    与拥有不同独特能力的同伴组成队伍。<br>    在没有使用任何武器的情况下进行战斗，利用环境保护自己，并为同伴找到武器，以保卫你。<br>    利用你的时光翻转装置为同伴开辟前进之路。&quot;<br><br>通过按一个按钮，随时在不同时间线之间来回切换。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807950/extras/b6827d49e5b2a353f23b134b6d5d2819.poster.avif?t=1753743460\" width=534 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807950/extras/b6827d49e5b2a353f23b134b6d5d2819.webm?t=1753743460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807950/extras/b6827d49e5b2a353f23b134b6d5d2819.mp4?t=1753743460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>一起合作，开辟前进之路。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807950/extras/4a7ff841d40d88b24883b8d0fc6170f3.poster.avif?t=1753743460\" width=534 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807950/extras/4a7ff841d40d88b24883b8d0fc6170f3.webm?t=1753743460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807950/extras/4a7ff841d40d88b24883b8d0fc6170f3.mp4?t=1753743460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>绑架者不会轻易放你离开，他们的动机不明确，但他们的敌对行动是明显的！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807950/extras/6eafcced4f15420703e83adcfaadf0ba.poster.avif?t=1753743460\" width=618 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807950/extras/6eafcced4f15420703e83adcfaadf0ba.webm?t=1753743460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807950/extras/6eafcced4f15420703e83adcfaadf0ba.mp4?t=1753743460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在不同时间线之间切换，寻找你的路径、隐藏的物品、囚犯以及许多奇怪的东西。你懂的，典型的《时光翻转器》情节。",
